
1. place schema under solr-5.3.1/example/techproducts/solr/techproducts/conf 

2. run updateSolr.sh for adding json format file and will automatically commit.
(please note that this updateSolr corresponds to the finaloutput2.json format.)

3. reload schema by re-running 
  $SOLR_HOME/bin/solr stop
  $SOLR_HOME/bin/solr -e techproducts

